Source: kernel-image-di
Section: debian-installer
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Joey Hess <joeyh@debian.org>
Standards-Version: 3.5.0.0
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 2.1.18), dpkg-dev (>= 1.7.0), kernel-source-2.4.1, kernel-package

Package: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Section: admin
Architecture: any
Provides: kernel-image
Depends: fileutils (>= 4.0)
Suggests: lilo (>= 19.1),  fdutils, kernel-doc-${kernel:Version}
Description: Linux kernel binary image for the Debian installer
 This package contains the Linux kernel image version ${kernel:Version},
 for the experimental Debian installer project. This kernel is very
 modular, and will only work on Debian systems that boot into an initrd.

Package: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}-udeb
Architecture: any
Provides: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Description: Linux kernel binary image for the Debian installer
 This package contains the Linux kernel image version ${kernel:Version},
 for the experimental Debian installer project. It does _not_ provide
 a usable kernel for your full Debian system.

Package: nic-modules-${kernel:Version}
Depends: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Architecture: any
Provides: 3c501.o, 3c503.o, 3c505.o, 3c507.o, 3c509.o, 3c515.o, 3c59x.o, 82596.o, eepro100.o, via-rhine.o, ne.o, ne2k-pci.o, tulip.o
Description: Common NIC drivers
 This package contains common NIC drivers for the linux kernel.

Package: serial-modules-${kernel:Version}
Depends: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Architecture: any
Provides: generic_serial.o
Description: Serial drivers
 This package contains serial drivers for the linux kernel.

Package: ppp-modules-${kernel:Version}
Depends: serial-modules-${kernel:Version}, kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Architecture: any
Provides: ppp_generic.o, ppp_async.o, ppp_synctty.o, ppp_deflate.o, pppox.o, pppoe.o
Description: PPP drivers
 This package contains PPP drivers for the linux kernel.

Package: isa-pnp-modules-${kernel:Version}
Depends: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Architecture: any
Provides: isa-pnp.o
Description: isa-pnp drivers
 This package contains isa-pnp drivers for the linux kernel.

Package: packet-socket-${kernel:Version}
Depends: kernel-image-${kernel:Version}
Architecture: any
Provides: af_packet.o
Description: packet protocol driver
 This package contains the packet socket driver, used by dhcp and other
 things that need raw network device access.
